data.description: Welcome to 5000 Northfield Court, a stunning home in Charleston, South Carolina. This residence is a true gem, offering ample space, privacy, and a touch of luxury. The recently renovated kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, perfect for creating delectable meals and hosting unforgettable gatherings. The updated master bathroom is a luxurious retreat, providing a serene space to unwind and rejuvenate. The fenced yard is a haven for children and pets, offering a safe and secure outdoor area to play and explore. With boat/RV parking available, you'll have the freedom to adventure and explore the beautiful surroundings. Additionally, a shed provides extra storage for all your belongings, ensuring a clutter-free living environment. Don't miss this elegant opportunity to own a truly exceptionalhome. Schedule a showing of your future home and experience the beauty and charm of 5000 Northfield Court for yourself starting on the 14th of April before it is too late! VA Assumable Loan at 2.75%
